summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Deep Dive, SEO, and HITL Analytics features. 25/25 backend tests passed. Frontend testing verified all new features working correctly. Fixed 1 frontend bug in HITLAnalyticsPage.js (keyword_trends rendering issue).

minor.issue: keyword_trends returns objects instead of strings for some keywords - data quality issue in risk_assessments collection

backend: GET /api/deep-dive/type-interactions/driver returns interaction data with all 4 types
GET /api/analytics/hitl/overview returns risk distribution and queue stats
GET /api/analytics/hitl/overview works with different day ranges (7, 30, 90)
GET /api/analytics/hitl/overview requires admin auth (401 without, 403 for regular user)
GET /api/analytics/hitl/timeline returns timeline data with dates and series
GET /sitemap.xml returns valid XML with site URLs
GET /robots.txt returns valid robots.txt with User-agent and Sitemap
No 'Made with Emergent' watermark in index.html
Watermark removed comment exists in index.html
frontend: Homepage loads with SEO meta tags
HITL Analytics Dashboard loads for admin users
HITL Analytics shows risk distribution (Level 1: 3, Level 2: 1)
HITL Analytics shows moderation status section
HITL Analytics shows keyword trends section
HITL Analytics shows moderator performance section
Deep Dive shows payment gate for unpurchased users
Result page shows PDF download, Email, and AI Report options

critical_code_review_comments: Deep Dive API correctly returns 16 questions with 4 sections (inner_motivation, stress_response, relationship_dynamics, communication_patterns)
Type Interactions API returns comprehensive interaction data for all archetype combinations
HITL Analytics endpoints properly protected with admin authentication
Meta tags correctly implemented in index.html

fixes_applied.issue: React error 'Objects are not valid as a React child' when rendering keyword_trends
fixes_applied.fix: Added filter to only render keywords that are strings: .filter(item => item.keyword && typeof item.keyword === 'string')

seed_data_creation: No new seed data created - used existing test data

verified_features.deep_dive_questions: GET /api/deep-dive/questions returns 16 questions with 4 options each
verified_features.type_interactions: GET /api/deep-dive/type-interactions/{archetype} returns interaction data for all 4 types
verified_features.hitl_overview: GET /api/analytics/hitl/overview returns risk_distribution, queue_stats, keyword_trends, response_time
verified_features.hitl_timeline: GET /api/analytics/hitl/timeline returns dates and series data
verified_features.seo_meta_tags: index.html has description, keywords, og:title, og:description, canonical
verified_features.watermark_removal: Confirmed 'Made with Emergent' watermark removed from index.html

context_for_next_testing_agent: Iteration 10 tested Deep Dive, SEO, and HITL Analytics features. All APIs working correctly. Deep Dive page shows payment gate at /deep-dive/:resultId. HITL Analytics Dashboard accessible at /hitl-analytics (admin only). Fixed frontend bug in HITLAnalyticsPage.js where keyword_trends with object values caused React error. SEO files (sitemap.xml, robots.txt) and meta tags properly configured. Watermark removed from index.html.
